---
title: All cost guides
description: Every North Texas cost guide we publish — researched price ranges for DFW home repairs and upgrades.
layout: base.njk
permalink: /guides/
---
<h1>All cost guides</h1>
<p class="lede">Every guide below is a researched range for the Dallas–Fort Worth market — not a quote, and not a lead form. Each one lists its sources and a last-updated date.</p>

{% if collections.guides.length %}
<div class="cards">
  {% for g in collections.guides %}
  <a class="card" href="{{ g.url }}">
    <h3>{{ g.data.title }}</h3>
    <p>{{ g.data.description }}</p>
    <span class="meta-row">
      {% if g.data.category %}<span class="tag">{{ g.data.category }}</span>{% endif %}
      <span class="updated">Updated {{ g.data.updated | readableDate }}</span>
    </span>
  </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
{% else %}
<p class="empty-note">First cost guides are in research now. Check back soon, or read <a href="/methodology/">how we price</a> in the meantime.</p>
{% endif %}
